OL,3,CCape Verde becomes smallest country to
OL,4,Cadvance to World Cup knockout rounds
OL,6,FCape Verde has defied odds to become
OL,7,Fthe smallest country by population to
OL,8,Fearn a spot in the men's World Cup
OL,9,Fknockout rounds.
OL,11,FThe Blue Sharks completed an
OL,12,Fimprobable run through the group stage
OL,13,Fafter drawing for a third time on
OL,14,FFriday night, with a 0-0 result
OL,15,Fagainst Saudi Arabia in Texas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
