OL,3,CCape Verde becomes smallest country to
OL,4,Cadvance to World Cup knockout rounds
OL,6,FPost-match, Cape Verde coach Bubista
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are proud of having arrived
OL,8,Fat this stage. We have shown that we
OL,9,Fare a small country, but that we fight
OL,10,Ffor the things that we want to
OL,11,Fachieve."
OL,13,FThe small island nation off the
OL,14,Fwestern coast of Africa has a
OL,15,Fpopulation of just over 500,000.
OL,17,FThe team are making their debut on
OL,18,Ffootball's grandest stage, and are
OL,19,Falso the first debutant since 2010 to
OL,20,Fmake it through to the knockouts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
