OL,3,CCape Verde becomes smallest country to
OL,4,Cadvance to World Cup knockout rounds
OL,6,FCape Verde advance after another
OL,7,Fstrong game from 40-year-old
OL,8,Fgoalkeeper Vozinha, whose tournament
OL,9,Fsuccess has helped him earn more than
OL,10,F16 million Instagram followers.
OL,12,F"We are small," Vozinha said, speaking
OL,13,Fabout the island nation, "but we have
OL,14,Fbig hearts and we are fighters."
OL,16,F"There is a lot of quality in our
OL,17,Fnational team," Vozinha said.
OL,19,F"Maybe for many of you, you think the
OL,20,FCape Verdean player is not good enough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782609481
OL,3,CCape Verde becomes smallest country to
OL,4,Cadvance to World Cup knockout rounds
OL,6,F"But we came here to show that we have
OL,7,Fa lot of quality and we are here to
OL,8,Fcompete and our players can play
OL,9,Feverywhere in the big competition, in
OL,10,Fthe big leagues."
OL,12,FThe team finished second in Group H on
OL,13,FFriday, with a 0-0 draw with Spain and
OL,14,Fa 2-2 result against Uruguay already
OL,15,Funder their belt.
OL,17,FThe group winners, Spain, beat Uruguay
OL,18,Fon Friday night and won the group.
