OL,3,CCape Verde becomes smallest country to
OL,4,Cadvance to World Cup knockout rounds
OL,6,FDrawing all three group matches
OL,7,Fdoesn't guarantee advancement at major
OL,8,Fsoccer tournaments, but several teams
OL,9,Fhave done it in the past, including
OL,10,FWales in 1958, Ireland and the
OL,11,FNetherlands in 1990, and Chile in 1998.
OL,13,FNew Zealand, however, also got three
OL,14,Fdraws at the 2010 World Cup and was
OL,15,Feliminated.
OL,17,FCape Verde advanced as their three
OL,18,Fdraws earned them three points, one
OL,19,Fmore than Saudi Arabia and Uruguay,
OL,20,Fwho each finished on two points.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
