OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1782609481
OL,3,CCape Verde becomes smallest country to
OL,4,Cadvance to World Cup knockout rounds
OL,6,FHaving led his squad to new heights,
OL,7,FBubista was asked if he could have
OL,8,Fimagined such a run entering the
OL,9,Ftournament.
OL,11,F"I've always said that sooner or later
OL,12,FCape Verde would be on such a stage,"
OL,13,Fhe said.
OL,15,FAdding: "Of course it's hard to have
OL,16,Fsuch a forecast, but I always knew."
OL,18,FCape Verde will play reigning World
OL,19,FCup champion Argentina in Miami on
OL,20,FJuly 3.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
